subject: Automobile Racing
organizations: National Assn of Stock Car Auto Racing
lead_paragraph: Kyle Busch passed Jimmie Johnson after a restart on the next-to-last lap Saturday night to claim his seventh Nascar Sprint Cup series victory of the season.
